On a family holiday and looked at places nearby I could potentially free dive. Found this, seal rocks. Although the visibility wasn’t amazing, the family and I had a great time looking around and seeing what was in the between the sea grass and rocks. Some big woobegongs and turtles of specific note.

## Dive stats

- **Location:** Seal Rocks
- **Date:** 20 November 2024

[Watch the full dive on YouTube](https://youtu.be/O_hwTAPrfJI)
